<refdata_subclause title="Independent_property_representation Default Value">
A <b>DefaultValue</b> is the value of the of a parameter, variable or option
in the case that no other value is specified.
<p>URI Specification</p>
<screen>
http://www.tc184-sc4.org/ts/10303/-233/taxonomy#DefaultValue
</screen>
</refdata_subclause>
